{"tid":913283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行尖嘴...法國香港變左好多..","createTime":"2018-11-23T09:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T04:53:23.000Z","uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f02397ed24ab7c6e920becb8b24572b916c2d16","tid":913283,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟今日就有D事去中港城<br />\n莫講成條街旅行團、鳩嗚同LEUNG到成陣中國除既男男女女....<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母入去一期禁錢,仲要望到前面隻支那雞...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等得耐都算....等等下望到....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老味 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">銀行戶口成1000萬</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n走個陣行去柯士甸,望到高鐵聳立於香港土地上....東邊係有D殘舊既舊城區咁...<br />\n突然覺得香港所謂既東方蜘蛛/一國兩制/金融之都....有種莫名其妙既唏噓....<br />\n為左賺祖国煩榮、賺銀紙..少少烏煙瘴氣,多多同胞,真係屌你老母赴湯蹈火再所不辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/di